        <abstract>
            <p>Sends birthday wishes.</p> 
<p>Comments on progress of CD’s theory in Germany. Mentions opposition of Rudolf Virchow and his reply <hi rend="italic">Freie Wissenschaft und freie Lehre</hi> [1878].</p> 
            <p>Describes research trip to Brittany and Normandy.</p> 
<p>Research on <hi rend="italic">Challenger</hi> Radiolaria.</p> 
        </abstract>
